case_circumstances: Jane Doe #07-99 was a homicide victim found as skeletal remains scattered below a mountainous road leading from the City Creek area (north San Bernardino) to Running Springs. Identity may only be established with dental X-rays, head X-rays or DNA (refer to CODIS # BK-04-000704).  Possible comparison with "smiling photographs" (showing teeth).
